pipe (specs_tests3)

 o: faninany |
    sort |
    specs 2-* 1 |
    cons ?

-- specs numberrange  ?
   literal one two   three    four five six |
   specs 12-24 1 |
   c1: compare any ~2# 1 specs numberrange  ~ equal ~*OK*~ notequal ~**FAIL**  at rec \\c col \\b.~ less /Less:\nActual:\n\\p\nExpected:\n\\s\n/ more /More:\nActual:\n\\p\nExpected:\n\\s\n/ |
   o: ?
   literal hree    four |
   c1: ?

